     C                     MOVE #R3,Z     RRN     70
     C                     SETOF                       82
     C                     MOVE @TOKCD    #KTOK   40
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    @TOKNM
     C           #KTOK     CHAINFGBPL011             82
